content.rendered:
Directed by Faraz Haider

Written by Mysskin

Cast Abhay Deol (Nanu). Patralekhaa Paul (Siddhi (as Patralekha Paul)). Rajesh Sharma (Siddhi’s Father). Himani Shivpuri (Nanu’s mother). Manu Rishi Chadha (Dabbu). Brijendra Kala (Kumar Bhaiya). Shefali Rana (Gayatri Bhabhi). Vipin k Sethie (Halavaee). Sapna Choudhary (Dancer- Song ‘Tere Thumke’ (as Sapna Chaudhary)). Shreya Narayan (Ghost Buster). Shadab Ahmad (Hospital surveillance in-charge). Manoj Pahwa (Fortuner Owner). Gurmeet Singh(Yahoo). Mahendra Shrivas (Halwayee). Spandan Chaturvedi (Phantom). Reshma Khan (Promilla). Adithi Kalkunte (Dagar’s Wife). Sameer Siddiqui (Mohit Dagar). Kunika Sadanand (Mrs. Nandi (as Kunickaa Sadanand)). Tarana Kaur (Psychiatrist). Sagar Singh(Old Man at Kothi #1) . Eshan Ali (Mad Man in Hospital). Faraz Haider (Biker). Mohammad Salman Khan (Salman). Alika Nair (Daughter of Secretary). Rakesh Bazad Raj (Ghost Buster’s Assistant). Vikash Rajput (Vikash Rajput). Zulfi Rajput (Rude Receptionist). Vivek Rana (Chimney Repairman). Chirag Sethi (Udhariya). Deepaq Sharma (Nabhaey). Kartik Sharma (Bartender)

Languages Hindi

Producers Bhanu Bhaskar. Ashwini Chaudhary. Wahi Harsh. Abhinav Jain. Digambber Hari Paatil. Sajid Qureshi. Rakesh Bazad Raj. Mahipal Karan Rathore

Production Inbox Pictures Pvt Ltd
